{"tid":1064160,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 西班牙拳手慘遭另一男子野外強姦逾15年 令人髮指","createTime":"2019-03-16T10:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T09:32:45.000Z","uid":90515,"like":292,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"b0dc42a2be3328c226de1a2efe40c8c21ce1c3ff","tid":1064160,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:28:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5tUiCgt6hoU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5tUiCgt6hoU&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=7bffb666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5tUiCgt6hoU</a><br />\n<br />\n[METOO]  31歲男受害人沙治奧拉莫斯報稱於2005至2019年間於西班牙慘遭現年31歲嫌疑人里奧美斯強姦逾數十次。據了解，男事主於賤種足球會從事職業拳手，因工作關係認識男嫌疑人，該男子每年約見男事主只少2次，每次均在數萬人旁觀及幾億人透過電視轉播見證下中出1至6次，情況令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n有花生團體指出案件並不屬於個別事件，反映賤種足球會仍有很多拳手慘遭類似毒手，包括比比、卡斯拿斯、馬些路等，希望當局重新審視情況。亦有評論指出該類案件能激發部份球迷腦內的安多芬，令人快樂<br />\n<br />\n文: C朗老母"},{"pid":"b914111e8004c86fbc0425c1bf849390b1eb8449","tid":1064160,"uid":232594,"like":11,"dislike":14,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:31:02.000Z","msg":"美斯咁細粒，似0仔多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e310c6b8fe2b88f094be5cf219c152c786358a1","tid":1064160,"uid":90515,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:31:20.000Z","msg":"條強姦犯真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63dd4f78ac7caa84b01fdf2b2c4dc2739d1a2b71","tid":1064160,"uid":180996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:33:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb68f898c25867ab1ba9f576099e0577e5cf21bc","tid":1064160,"uid":70201,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T10:34:10.000Z","msg":"一心諗住入嚟睇gay porn 點知原來係撚狗虐畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c580e51fc69b8708c3e82